on to non-existent document` and `should reject connection to invalid path` - those don't need message receipt. The failing ones all timeout on `waitForMessage`.\n\nLet me write a minimal test to debug:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3535,"cache_read_input_tokens":71351,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3535},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"683b7004-71e2-42a0-bc85-5b5277d63d2f","uuid":"5ee505fc-45da-4bb2-b104-1461b604f516"}
